      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this lovely ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really nice shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without breaking the bank. It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
