      "description": "This A80-generation powerhouse features the venerable 2JZ-GTE twin-sequential turbocharged inline-six, delivering a broad powerband and exceptional thermal efficiency. Power is managed via the sought-after Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox and delivered to the tarmac through a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its precision-engineered double-wishbone suspension geometry, offering flat cornering and communicative feedback. Meticulously maintained to preserve mechanical tolerances, this example boasts a clean engine bay, crisp gear synchronization, and a robust forced-induction system. It represents a prime opportunity for an enthusiast seeking a high-performance analog legend with uncompromised structural integrity.",
